t the ocean of tears, and fell off the boat into the deeps.  <BR> calling out for any form of life, I found the only other survivor-- another rogue, who had also hidden prior to the attack. <BR> its times like this when a Rogue is happy to be alive and who she is. <BR>  <BR>    <p>Jete D'PaintedToes
of the Jesters
of Tarew Marr
